OL,5,G2230 When Comedy Goes Horribly Wrong
OL,6,     FJulian Clary narrates this look at
OL,7,     Fcomedy going horribly wrong on an
OL,8,     Fepic scale, featuring some of the
OL,9,     Fnation's best-loved funny men and
OL,10,     Fwomen.
OL,11,G0030 Scandal!: When Sven Scored with
OL,12,G     Ulrika
OL,13,     FThe story that stunned the UK as,
OL,14,     Fduring the 2002 World Cup, it was
OL,15,     Frevealed that England football
OL,16,     Fmanager Sven-Goran Eriksson was
OL,17,     F'playing away' with compatriot
OL,18,     FUlrika Jonsson.
